4. Triggers notification by calling `valueChanged()` on the target
5. Uses `ThreadManager` to ensure all notification tasks are processed
6. Returns a pair containing the notification status and call count

The function follows the exact steps specified and uses the appropriate `reaction` library functions as requested.

